Note: also reported via Connect to Visual Studio bug reports.

EmsiSoft AV 7.0.0.25 (latest updates installed) reports two infections in TypeScript 0.09 downloaded from: http://www.microsoft.com/en-us/download/details.aspx?id=34790

Report:

Emsisoft Anti-Malware v. 7.0.0.25

ID Object
0 C:\Program Files (x86)\Microsoft Visual Studio 11.0\Common7\IDE\CommonExtensions\Microsoft\TypeScript\ScriptExecutionEnvironment.dll
Gen:Variant.Symmi.17133 (B)

1 C:\Program Files (x86)\Microsoft Visual Studio 11.0\Common7\IDE\VWDExpressExtensions\TypeScript\ScriptExecutionEnvironment.dll
Gen:Variant.Symmi.17133 (B)

Of course these could be false positives, and they have been reported to EmsiSoft for evaluation.

thanks, Bill
